   Coarsely mash the egg whites with a fork. Add the mayonnaise,
mustard, green onions, celery, tarragon, pepper and optional salt;
mix well. Use immediately or refrigerate overnight.

   6 to 8 servings. Each of 8 servings: 485 calories; 415 mg sodium;
125 mg cholesterol; 28 grams fat; 17 grams saturated fat; 55 grams
carbohydrates; 5 grams protein; 2.21 grams fiber.

   4 to 6 servings. Each of 6 servings: 204 calories; 359 mg sodium;
19 mg cholesterol; 8 grams fat; 3 grams saturated fat; 25 grams
carbohydrates; 9 grams protein; 4.84 grams fiber.

   4 to 8 servings. Each of 8 servings:  328 calories; 212 mg sodium;
72 mg cholesterol; 22 grams fat; 9 grams saturated fat; 10 grams
carbohydrates; 22 grams protein; 2 grams fiber.

